snippet.textDisplay:
One of the maddest chord progressions .. bloody hell .. how do they come up with such stuff .. 
For all those looking to play : Umair's part starts with C#maj (combine with F#), then first magical shift happens at "kaisa dil pe waar kiya re" which is Emaj.. and then in Balouch's part (the mukhda) , we move to a C#minor progression .. So, chords are pretty simple, no altered tuning needed (as for some coke studio songs) but the way the song moves in it's mood is outstanding.
Awesome feel .. play on fellas and have fun :) 
Love, 
Prajesh
